name: wardow.com
tag_list: bags, handbags, leatherbags, trolleys, accessories, suitcase
overview:
wardow.com offers exclusive and high-class processed bags, handbags, suitcases, trolleys and accessories from the premium and luxury segment of international designer and brands. We offer only products in best, proven quality with original certificates and at attractive conditions. First-class service, wide product range and your satisfaction as a customer is our top priority.

In 2005, the founder launched wardow.com with the focus on exclusive “Bags & Lifestyle” and created therefore an insider tip for rare Italian luxury fashion brands at good prices. Today it has become one of the best assorted online shops in the high-quality bags and luggage area!
